      "span_text": "In the original definition, both events must have wide enough scopes; in the new version, the events (say e 1 and e 2 ) may also synchronise if e 1 's scope is wide enough to reach e 2 and e 1 is remote, or if e 2 's scope is wide enough to reach e 1 and e 2 is remote."
